---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
description: A digital museum of design styles - Explore authentic design style demonstrations and learn through real examples
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <h1 class="hero-title">A <span class="highlight-brutal">digital museum</span> of design styles</h1>
    <p class="hero-description">
      Explore authentic design style demonstrations and learn the history, principles, and techniques behind iconic visual movements.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-md justify-center mt-xl">
      <a href="/gallery/" class="button button-brutal">Explore Gallery</a>
      <a href="/submit/" class="button button-secondary">Submit Your Design</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="wrapper">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-xl text-brutal">Featured Design Styles</h2>

  {% if designStyles and designStyles.length > 0 %}
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      {% for style in designStyles %}
        {% if style.featured or loop.index <= 3 %}
          <a href="/gallery/{{ style.slug.current }}/" class="gallery-card">
            {% if style.sampleImages and style.sampleImages.length > 0 %}
              <img
                src="{{ style.sampleImages[0].asset._ref | replace('image-', 'https://cdn.sanity.io/images/' + site.sanityProjectId + '/' + site.sanityDataset + '/') | replace('-jpg', '.jpg') | replace('-png', '.png') }}"
                alt="{{ style.sampleImages[0].alt or style.title }}"
                class="gallery-card-image"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            {% else %}
              <div class="gallery-card-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000 0%, #333 100%); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                <span style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em;">{{ style.title | upper | truncate(10, true, '') }}</span>
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="gallery-card-content">
              <p class="gallery-card-tag">Design Style</p>
              <h3>{{ style.title }}</h3>
              <p>{{ style.description }}</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <div class="text-center">
      <p>No design styles available yet. Check back soon!</p>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</section>

<section class="wrapper mt-3xl">
  <div class="grid grid-2">
    <div class="shadow-brutal" style="padding: var(--spacing-lg); border: var(--border-brutal) solid var(--color-primary);">
      <h2 class="text-brutal">Learn Through Authentic Examples</h2>
      <p>
        MyWebClass.org is an educational platform that teaches design history through fully-implemented website demonstrations. Each style in our gallery represents careful research and authentic recreation of historical design movements.
      </p>
      <p>
        From Swiss International Style to modern interpretations, explore how design principles translate into real-world applications.
      </p>
      <a href="/about/" class="button button-secondary mt-md">Learn More</a>
    </div>

    <div class="shadow-brutal" style="padding: var(--spacing-lg); border: var(--border-brutal) solid var(--color-primary);">
      <h2 class="text-brutal">Contribute Your Work</h2>
      <p>
        Are you a student or designer passionate about design history? Submit your own style-accurate demos to our gallery. Share your interpretation of classic design movements and help build this educational resource.
      </p>
      <p>
        All submissions are reviewed by instructors for historical accuracy and authenticity before being added to the public gallery.
      </p>
      <a href="/submit/" class="button button-brutal mt-md">Submit Design</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
